OL,3,CSouth East Water CEO David Hinton
OL,4,Cstill "has no plans to resign" over
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,FThe Chief Executive of South East
OL,8,FWater has told ITV Meridian he wants
OL,9,Fto deliver a plan which will benefit
OL,10,Fcustomers and he has "no plans to
OL,11,Fresign" over water outages which left
OL,12,Ftens of thousands of people with no
OL,13,Fsupplies.
OL,15,FDavid Hinton apologised again for the
OL,16,Floss of supplies in Kent and Sussex,
OL,17,Fbut said there is a plan in place
OL,18,Fwhich will protect supply for
OL,19,Fcustomers in the future.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/14
