OL,3,CSouth East Water CEO David Hinton
OL,4,Cstill "has no plans to resign" over
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian's Matt Teale
OL,8,Fhe reiterated that the issues
OL,9,Faffecting homes and businesses in the
OL,10,Frun up to Christmas, and in the New
OL,11,FYear were down to a combination of
OL,12,Ffreezing weather, and the storm which
OL,13,Fleft frozen and burst pipes.
OL,15,F"I really want to apologise
OL,16,Funreservedly for having a second round
OL,17,Fof interruption to supply," he began.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/14
