OL,3,CSouth East Water CEO David Hinton
OL,4,Cstill "has no plans to resign" over
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,F"Water is an absolutely essential
OL,8,Fservice and I know the impact it has
OL,9,Fon customers, businesses and the
OL,10,Fcommunity, and for that interruption,
OL,11,Fthe repeated interruption, I'm deeply
OL,12,Fsorry.
OL,14,F"We saw an increase in leakage of
OL,15,Faround 60 million litres pretty much
OL,16,Fovernight - we produce about 540
OL,17,Fmillion litres, so that's a big
OL,18,Fincrease in one day.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
