OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1769541167
OL,3,CSouth East Water CEO David Hinton
OL,4,Cstill "has no plans to resign" over
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,F"We were coping with that as a
OL,8,Fcompany, but then it was followed
OL,9,Fimmediately by the storm, which had
OL,10,Ftwo impacts for us. One is it made the
OL,11,FRiver Ouse effectively semi-treatable.
OL,12,FWe could not treat it at its normal
OL,13,Flevel, and our main treatment was
OL,14,FBarkham near the south coast.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
