OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1769541167
OL,3,CSouth East Water CEO David Hinton
OL,4,Cstill "has no plans to resign" over
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,F"Output went down, so we had a
OL,8,Fcombination of both demand going up
OL,9,Fand supply going down. Similarly in
OL,10,FKent, Southern Water, we get a lot of
OL,11,Four water from, had issues their side
OL,12,Fboth because of the storm and the
OL,13,Ffreeze.
OL,15,F"And so we had less water from
OL,16,FSouthern, so that was also supply went
OL,17,Fdown and demand went up. So that
OL,18,Fstressed the system."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/14
