OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1769541167
OL,3,CSouth East Water CEO David Hinton
OL,4,Cstill "has no plans to resign" over
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,F"Not having water is so inconvenient,
OL,8,Fit really does impact lives in a big
OL,9,Fway.
OL,11,F"And again, that is what I'm
OL,12,Fabsolutely concentrating on, is
OL,13,Fgetting the water."
OL,15,FIt's estimated that businesses in
OL,16,FTunbridge Wells have lost a combined
OL,17,Ftotal of somewhere between #10 million
OL,18,Fand #20 million because of the South
OL,19,FEast Water crisis.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/14
