OL,4,Cstill "has no plans to resign" over
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,FThat's according to the MP for
OL,8,FTunbridge Wells, Mike Martin, who has
OL,9,Fnow launched an online consultation
OL,10,Ffor local businesses to share the
OL,11,Flosses they suffered during the
OL,12,Foutages.
OL,14,FAsked about compensation Mr Hinton
OL,15,Fsaid: "I've not seen that data, but I
OL,16,Fhave offered, that the company will
OL,17,Flook at this. The model in the UK,
OL,18,Fparticularly for utilities, where this
OL,19,Fhappens is the government set this
OL,20,Fkind of fairness regime via the GSS,
OL,21,Fthe Guaranteed Standard Service regime.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
