OL,3,CSouth East Water CEO David Hinton
OL,4,Cstill "has no plans to resign" over
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,F"And that's what's in play at the
OL,8,Fmoment, so that is the main route for
OL,9,Fcompensation in the UK utilities
OL,10,Fmarket.
OL,12,F"All customers and all businesses will
OL,13,Freceive their guaranteed standard
OL,14,Fservice compensation, which in some
OL,15,Fcases is up to two or three years of
OL,16,Fannual water bill.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/14
