OL,3,CSouth East Water CEO David Hinton
OL,4,Cstill "has no plans to resign" over
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,F"That was recently adjusted by the
OL,8,Fgovernment and is now the one that's
OL,9,Fin force for this kind of incident,
OL,10,Fand we also, for the previous
OL,11,Fincident, allocated #600,000 of extra
OL,12,Fmonies for businesses around the
OL,13,FChristmas period who we knew would be
OL,14,Fsuffering from a cash flow issue.
OL,16,F"We also paid that money as fast as
OL,17,Fpossible for that very reason."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/14
