OL,7,FMr Hinton did not attend a meeting at
OL,8,FTunbridge Wells Borough Council on
OL,9,FMonday night, being accused of a lack
OL,10,Fof accountability.
OL,12,FResponding he said: "No, we are
OL,13,F(meeting), and we've got in the diary
OL,14,Fanother round of stakeholder meetings,
OL,15,Fand we're going to do a lot of those.
OL,17,F"We really want to talk to the local
OL,18,Fcommunity about what we've learned.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/14
