OL,3,CSouth East Water CEO David Hinton
OL,4,Cstill "has no plans to resign" over
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,F"The meeting this week was, just a bit
OL,8,Ftoo soon for us to gather the
OL,9,Flearnings and have a really good
OL,10,Fdiscussion, a really meaningful
OL,11,Fdiscussion with our stakeholders and
OL,12,Flocal communities.
OL,14,F"So we didn't cancel it by any stretch.
OL,16,F"We proposed the timeframe by which we
OL,17,Fshould have the second meeting or the
OL,18,Fnew meeting, and we very much got
OL,19,Fthose in the diary.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/14
