OL,3,CSouth East Water CEO David Hinton
OL,4,Cstill "has no plans to resign" over
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,F"We're planning to go out and talk to
OL,8,Fthe communities and be very
OL,9,Faccountable and very visible in front
OL,10,Fof those communities."
OL,12,F"The main reason their bills are going
OL,13,Fup is to provide the resilience
OL,14,Fexpenditure that we desperately need,"
OL,15,Fhe said.
OL,17,F"The regulators agree to a certain
OL,18,Famount of resilience expenditure to
OL,19,Fsecure up Sussex and Kent, and that
OL,20,Fdrives a big part of that bill
OL,21,Fincrease.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/14
