OL,3,CSouth East Water CEO David Hinton
OL,4,Cstill "has no plans to resign" over
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,F"We are effectively catching up a
OL,8,Flittle bit on some of the resilience
OL,9,Fthat should have been in place, and so
OL,10,Fthat's really driving the bill
OL,11,Fincreases.
OL,13,F"It's money that customers are paying
OL,14,Fto improve the resilience of the
OL,15,Fnetwork.
OL,17,F"We've talked to customers and they're
OL,18,Freally supportive of this investment."
